With a huge crystal chandelier showcased in the center of the floor and a few cute table spaces, they make for a more feminine ambiance. Occasions like birthdays, bachelorette parties, and the like. But if you're going because of one of those occasions and have a big group, make sure you plan it with them well and know exactly your head count. We were tightly packed and the service felt unaccommodating when 2-3 extra people dropped by for a drink after dinner.
